Description.Text: Time of day in HH:MM or H:MM 24-hour format per UTC time zone.
Slice Differentiator If not needed, the value can be set to FFFFFF.
Slice/Service Type. Values 0 to 127 belong to standardized SST range and are defined in 3GPP TS 23.501. Values 128 to 255 belong to operator-specific range.
